name: Violetta Necklace
description:
This elegant and beautiful necklace is hand crafted using a striking amethyst, which I found in Italy, a coin pearl and small freshwater pearls which embellish the sterling sliver chain and clasp 

Please note that this necklace has a magnetic clasp, which makes it very easy to put on (my favorite), however this cannot be used by someone who has a pacemaker.

This necklace measures 19 inches.

Please contact me if you have any questions.
